OL,3,CCrispin Odey banned from working in
OL,4,Cfinance and fined #1.8m
OL,6,FHedge fund manager Crispin Odey has
OL,7,Fbeen fined #1.8 million and banned
OL,8,Ffrom the UK finance industry for a
OL,9,F"lack of integrity," over his handling
OL,10,Fof sexual harassment allegations
OL,11,Flevelled against him.
OL,13,FIn a provisional decision released by
OL,14,Fthe Financial Conduct Authority (FCA),
OL,15,Fthey said Mr Odey "repeatedly sought
OL,16,Fto evade and obstruct efforts to hold
OL,17,Fhim to account."
