OL,3,CCrispin Odey banned from working in
OL,4,Cfinance and fined #1.8m
OL,6,FThe investment management and advisory
OL,7,Ffirm founded by Mr Odey in 1991 made
OL,8,Fheadlines for its large bets against
OL,9,Fthe British economy, making hundreds
OL,10,Fand millions of pounds from the Brexit
OL,11,Fvote in 2016.
OL,13,FThe FCA found that his firm Odey Asset
OL,14,FManagement (OAM) could not deal
OL,15,Feffectively with complaints of
OL,16,Finappropriate conduct towards female
OL,17,Fmembers of staff because he
OL,18,Fcontinually threatened and intervened
OL,19,Fin the process.
