OL,6,FMr Odey has said he will challenge the
OL,7,FFCA's decision.
OL,9,FMr Odey has been at the centre of
OL,10,Fsexual misconduct allegations after a
OL,11,Freport in the Financial Times (FT)
OL,12,Fnewspaper uncovered claims from
OL,13,Fseveral women who had worked with him
OL,14,For known him.
OL,16,FThe women claimed they had been abused
OL,17,For harassed by him, with some alleging
OL,18,Fhe sexually assaulted them.
