OL,3,CCrispin Odey banned from working in
OL,4,Cfinance and fined #1.8m
OL,6,FMr Odey has previously denied the
OL,7,Fallegations against him, telling the
OL,8,FFT they were "rubbish".
OL,10,FIn May, he sued the FT for libel
OL,11,Fseeking almost #80 million in damages.
OL,13,FOn Monday, the watchdog said it had
OL,14,Fdecided Mr Odey was not a fit and
OL,15,Fproper person to hold any role related
OL,16,Fto regulated finance activities.
