OL,6,FTherese Chambers, the FCA's director
OL,7,Fof enforcement and market oversight,
OL,8,Fsaid: "A culture of silence in which
OL,9,Fallegations of misconduct are not
OL,10,Fdealt with effectively can put
OL,11,Fconsumers and markets at risk.
OL,13,F"Mr Odey repeatedly sought to evade
OL,14,Fand obstruct efforts to hold him to
OL,15,Faccount.
OL,17,F"His lack of integrity means he
OL,18,Fdeserves to be banned from the
OL,19,Findustry."
