OL,3,CCrispin Odey banned from working in
OL,4,Cfinance and fined #1.8m
OL,6,FBetween 2021 and 2022, OAM tried to
OL,7,Finvestigate inappropriate behaviour
OL,8,Fand discipline Mr Odey.
OL,10,FThis incorporated numerous allegations
OL,11,Fof sexual harassment of female members
OL,12,Fof staff between 2003 and 2020, and an
OL,13,Fallegation of sexual assault in 2005.
OL,15,FIt also looked into what it deemed
OL,16,Finappropriate behaviour, including
OL,17,Ftouching staff, taking unaccompanied
OL,18,Ffemale members of staff to lunch or on
OL,19,Fshopping trips, and messaging them
OL,20,Foutside of work.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
