OL,3,CCrispin Odey banned from working in
OL,4,Cfinance and fined #1.8m
OL,6,FBut Mr Odey used his position as the
OL,7,Fmajority shareholder of OAM to remove
OL,8,Fmembers of its executive committee and
OL,9,Fappoint himself as its sole member,
OL,10,Fmeaning he could decide a disciplinary
OL,11,Fhearing into his conduct could be
OL,12,F"indefinitely postponed", the FCA
OL,13,Ffound.
