OL,3,CCrispin Odey banned from working in
OL,4,Cfinance and fined #1.8m
OL,6,FThis happened on two occasions,
OL,7,Fmeaning the hearing was not held until
OL,8,Fa year after it had been originally
OL,9,Fscheduled.
OL,11,FThe regulator said Mr Odey showed a
OL,12,F"reckless disregard" for OAM's
OL,13,Fgovernance and caused the company to
OL,14,Fbreach rules in order to protect his
OL,15,Fown interests.
OL,17,FIn March 2022, when Mr Odey appointed
OL,18,Fhimself as the sole committee member
OL,19,Ffor the second time, OAM managed
OL,20,Faround #2.8 billion worth of funds.
